Sylhet,  Moulvibazar are different districts. They say Sylheti Dialect.

Fultola, Sonapati are in places in Khulna, They speak Khulna or South dialect

snippet.textDisplay:
Foreigner who don't understand: 

Our buses are not so maintained..  People often jumps into crowd and the roads are not so good, often with broken parts. Buses has no distinct stopages, and they take passengers from anywhere, and go very slow. Thus people travels by standing in crowd and bus going slow.. This is called "Murir Tin" or "Puffed Rice Can".. As the bus looks like a big can😁😁😁
